General Manager – Online Services – E-Commerce
Adecco
Abu Dhabi, UAE
Posted on: 3 May 2014
THE ROLE
Expand all
Our client is launching a new service online in Abu Dhabi. They are looking for the General Manager of this new business. someone who can launch the product, work on its construction, communication....
The General Manager is in charge of planing, directing, and coordinating the operations of the company.
Duties and responsibilities include formulating policies, managing daily operations, and planning the use of materials and human resources.
REQUIREMENTS
Qualifications:
•Experience in Managing an online service business is a must.
•Knowledge of Abu Dhabi.
•Good decision maker.
•Ability to manage a team.
•Customer service oriented - Always looking for clients satisfaction.
ABOUT THE COMPANY
The Adecco Group is the world's leading provider of HR solutions. With more than 33,000 FTE employees and a network of 5,600 branches, in over 60 countries and territories around the world, we offer a wide variety of services, connecting close to 750,000 associates with well over 100,000 clients every day.
The services we offer fall into the broad categories of temporary staffing, permanent placement, career transition, talent development and workforce management solutions, as well as outsourcing and consulting.
The Adecco Group is based in Zurich-Glattbrugg, Switzerland and we are a Fortune Global 500 company listed on the SIX Swiss Exchange.
